news.news: Theis closed Wednesday's 119-108 loss to the Heat with zero points (0-1 FG, 0-1 3Pt), three rebounds, one assist and two blocks over 18 minutes.
news.analysis: Theis continued to play a limited role off the bench behind impressive rookie Yves Missi. Theis has scored in double-digits just once this season, averaging a very modest 3.7 points and 3.7 rebounds in 14.7 minutes per game.
